data.description: Wow! Country living, yet not far from the city! 1.47 acre home in the highly sought Rio Vista Subdivision! This subdivision sits on the outskirt of town near Valley Ranch Town Center, where there is an abundance of retail and dining for your convenience. This subdivision is a 30 minute drive to the airport, a 20 minute drive to retail shops and 15 minute drive to Big Rivers Waterpark. This 4 bedroom/3 bath home features a split floor plan, tray ceilings and high ceilings, arched entryways and crown molding throughout. The kitchen offers an abundant amount of cabinet space, a large island, granite counter-tops, and a large walk-in pantry. In the family room you can enjoy the natural light from the large picture windows. The outside of the home features a larger lot with plenty of backyard space and front yard space and the long driveway provides plenty of space for multiple vehicles. Come check it out and make it your new home for the Holiday's!
